%F A104562 T(n, k) = Sum_{j=0..n} (-1)^(k-j)*(-1)^((n-j)/2) C((n+j)/2, j)(1+(-1)^(n+j))C(j, k)/2.
%F A104562 T(n,k) = (-1)^(n-k)*A101950(n,k). - _Philippe Deléham_, Feb 19 2012
